---
title: Lemon Ricotta Pancakes with Cherry Maple Syrup, Walnuts, & Lemony Crème Fraîche | Serves 4
description: Over here, we think brunch is a food group—and a really important and scrumptious one. Today’s fix: decadent lemon ricotta pancakes and a dollop of zesty crème fraîche. Ready to take it to the next level? You’ll drizzle cherry maple syrup and sprinkle crunchy walnuts all over. Feel free to break out the special plates or just enjoy this meal in your PJs.
